Package com.pandora.calculation.repositories

package com.pandora.calculation.repositories
This package contains service interfaces and implementations for managing calculation repositories.
Version:
0.0.1
Author:
Wim Joost van Hoek
  • Class
    Description
    CalculationResultMemoryRepository
    This interface defines the contract for a repository responsible for handling memory operations related to calculation results.
    CalculationResultMemoryRepositoryImpl
    This repository class implements the CalculationResultMemoryRepository interface to provide memory storage and retrieval functionality for calculation results.

    An interface representing a repository for saving discharge data.
